        {
            "type": "heading",
            "comment": "Heading block",
            "text": "① Equip and Assembly"
        },

        {
            "type": "columns",
            "comment": "Two-column layout test",

            "columns": [
                [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "comment": "Overview paragraph",
                        "text": "Equip the Panzerfaust 30 or Panzerfaust 60 under the Launcher Slot from the Spearhead DLC.\nMake sure it is loaded by checking to see if the tube has the grenade on the end, if not then the tubed is used, and cannot be reloaded. If you are unable to fire, make sure the tube has the Warhead Panzerfaust round within the ammo slot. If it is not, but the tube is unfired, it may appear as if the tube is ready to fire, but without the round, it is unable to do so."
                    }
                ],

                [

